section.name: Course Conclusion
section.summary:
We are dedicated to creating excellent self-paced courses. Your responses to the following questions will help us improve our course design, instruction, and the type of services we are able to offer online participants.

We appreciate you completing the short evaluation. Most of the questions only require you to click on an answer, but there is room for your comments at the end.

Don't forget to download your certificate of completion after you finish the evaluation.
